    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel temporary. it feels like the only thing that's actually real about my life. you talk about \"surviving\" like it's a goal, but what if i'm just tired of surviving? wouldn't it be more honest to just admit that sometimes life is just too much and there isn't a way to make it better?",
